Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE Victorian Retail Investments in conjunction with Gorman Kelly are pleased to present for sale, under instructions from the Vendors, the opportunity to acquire the iconic "Stotts Corner" retail and office freehold located at the popular Glenferrie and Riversdale Road junction, within the affluent inner city suburb of Hawthorn.

The offering comprises a fully occupied two (2) level freestanding building securely leased to three quality tenants plus Optus rooftop income.

The key features of the property can be summarised as follows:

524-532 Glenferrie Road, Hawthorn:

* Prominent two (2) level freestanding building with over 45 metres of frontage onto the busy Glenferrie & Riversdale Roads
* Fully leased to three quality tenants plus Optus rooftop income
* Rare long term 5 year* Weighted Average Lease Expiry (WALE)
* Substantial building area of 696 sqm* with onsite parking and rear access
* Over 578 sqm* of prime Hawthorn land
* Current passing income of $226,124 per annum plus outgoings and GST
* Excellent location in close proximity to public transport, Monash Freeway/Citylink Camberwell Junction, Swinburne University and Glenferrie Road retail precinct
* Servicing one of Melbourne's most affluent and desirable locales
* Future redevelopment and/or subdivision potential (STCA)
*approx

The property is being offered to the market via On-site Public Auction Wednesday 11th December 2013 at 12.00pm. To obtain further information, or to arrange an inspection, please contact the sales and marketing agents.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Iconic Stotts Corner Freestanding Hawthorn Investment - 524-532 Glenferrie Rd, Hawthorn

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE Melbourne Strip Retail Investments and KYPA Property are proud to present to the market, 95 Burwood Road, Hawthorn.

We summarise the property details below, for your reference:

 - An exceptional two (2) level double fronted building (7.8m* frontage) with separate access to first floor dwelling

 - An underutilised landholding of 260sqm* including four (4) car parks on-title, complimented by highly accessible rear lane access via Elgin Place (7.8m* frontage)

 - Immediate capacity to add value to the rear of the site with approved permits for a four (4) level development

 - An unparalleled location just 4.5km* from the CBD and serviced by multiple public transport options

 - Positioned in one of Melbourne’s most lucrative and sought after suburbs, Hawthorn, with a median house price over $2,050,000*

*approx

•Three (3) separate tenancies providing a diverse annual income of $117,520*

•Freehold landholding of 172sqm* with rear lane access
